Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; brw extension force-install + auto-update for Chromium on Windows.
; Import with: reg import brw-chromium-policy.reg  (or double-click).
; For Google Chrome, replace "Chromium" with "Google\Chrome" in the key path.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Chromium\ExtensionInstallForcelist]
